Package musichub.business

Class Playlist

  • java.lang.Object
    • musichub.business.Playlist
  • public class Playlist
extends Object
    A Playlist object contains a list of songs and audio books from the librairy.

    A playlist can be added and removed from the librairy, and can be edited to add or remove elements from its list.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Sylvain BUI, Maxence LECLERC, Nour-El-Houda LOUATY, Sarra MADAD
    See Also:
    PlaylistList, Element, Chanson, LivreAudio
